      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a reliable companion that\u2019s ready for all your daily adventures! This car is in fair condition and shows some character from its time on the road, but it remains a solid, dependable performer that gets the job done. It's a fantastic opportunity to own a well-loved vehicle that still has plenty of life left at a great price!",
