    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone looking for a solid daily driver. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including some noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few small stains, but the cabin remains functional and comfortable. Mechanically, it has been well-maintained for its age, though it may require some minor routine service soon. It's a great choice for someone who prioritizes utility and reliability over a perfect appearance.",
