      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for those seeking a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several medium-sized dents and some fading in the paint, particularly on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows noticeable wear and some staining, but all essential features like the air conditioning and radio remain operational. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been consistently serviced, though it may require minor maintenance soon to address typical high-mileage wear. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone prioritizing utility and reliability over a perfect appearance.",
      "price": 23500.0,
