      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained in truly mint condition. Every aspect of this motorcar has been preserved to the highest standards, offering a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a specimen of unparalleled quality. From its flawless coachwork to its pristine cabin, this vehicle stands as a testament to meticulous ownership and remains in showroom state. Experience the zenith of automotive excellence with this peerless offering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
